Former hostage in Lebanon: "The return is quite complex to manage"
Kidnapped in Beirut on 8 March 1986 with three members of his "Antenne 2" team who had come to film a Hezbollah demonstration, journalist Jean-Louis Normandin was released nearly 21 months later, on 27 November 1987.
