"Le Nouvel Observateur" questioned Jean-Louis Normandin, 62, former reporter, retired since 2008, president of the association "Hostages of the world".
From the evening of your release, you were on the set of the 20h of "Antenne 2".
What are your memories of your liberation today?
On the spot in particular, in Beirut.
When I am released, I find myself in the trunk of a car where I meet - without seeing him because it is dark - Roger Auque.
